  {
    "title": "Story",
    "depth": 0,
    "paragraphs": [
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "\"Forest hunter with a Smilodon\""
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "sentences": [
          {
            "text": "A jungle orphan raised by a smilodon, was rescued by Leonin Nana when she was almost caught by a human slave trader.",
            "links": [
              {
                "type": "internal",
                "page": "Nana"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": "With the help of Nana, she learned the human language and fighting skills, but she still didn't trust humans and only trusted her friend, a little tiger named Leo."
          }
        ]
      }
